CheckNotifier, HarvestAgentListener
public class HarvestCoordinatorNotifier
extends java.lang.Object
implements HarvestAgentListener, CheckNotifier

The HarvestCoordinatorNotifier uses SOAP to send messages back to the core. These include notifications, heartbeats and job completions messages.
